.TH ASKCC "" "" "Environmental Variable"
.PC "Force prompting for CC names"
\fBASKCC=\fIYES/NO\fR
.PP
The environmental variable
.B ASKCC
directs the mailer program
.B mail
to prompt for carbon-copy names.
A carbon-copy (or CC) name gives another person to whom a mail message should
be sent.
To turn on prompting, use the command:
.DM	
	export ASKCC=YES
.DE
.SH "See Also"
.Xr "environmental variables," environva
.Xr mail mail.c
